---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const sriApplyUrl = 'https://unmask.nikkicates.com/reset-inquiry';
---

<Layout
  title="Strategic Reset Intensive | Strategic Transformations"
  description="A curated cohort experience for professional women navigating career transitions, economic uncertainty, and AI adoption. Walk away with a personal strategy, AI confidence, and a clear next step."
  section="st"
  accentColor="teal"
>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[88vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#0f172a]"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 70% at 65% 45%, rgba(13,148,136,0.09) 0%, transparent 65%), radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 5% 85%, rgba(15,76,122,0.1) 0%, transparent 55%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px]" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 5%, #0d9488 25%, #0d9488 75%, transparent 95%);"></div>

    <div class="container-wide relative z-10 py-20 md:py-28">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">

        <!-- Left: Core message -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-6">
            <span class="st-tag inline-flex">Strategic Transformations</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-muted border border-border rounded-full px-3 py-1">
              B2P · Professional Women in Transition
            </span>
          </div>

          <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-light leading-[1.06] mb-6 animate-on-scroll" style="font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5.5vw, 4.2rem);">
            Strategic<br/>
            <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT">Reset Intensive</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="font-body text-xl text-light leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.08s">
            You are not behind. You are in between.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-lg text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
            Career transitions in an unstable economy feel disorienting because they are. The rules have changed. AI is reshaping entire industries. And the old roadmap no longer applies.
          </p>
          <p class="font-body text-base text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.16s">
            The Strategic Reset Intensive is a curated small-group cohort for professional women who are ready to stop reacting and start building. You will leave with a personal and professional strategy, real AI tools you actually know how to use, and the clarity to move forward with intention.
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
            <a href={sriApplyUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-teal text-base !py-3.5 !px-7">
              Apply for the Next Cohort
              <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#what-you-get" class="btn-outline-teal text-base !py-3.5">
              See What Is Included
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Quick facts card -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-5 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.25s">
          <div class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/30 p-8">
            <p class="font-heading text-light text-lg font-semibold mb-6">The SRI at a Glance</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              {[
                { label: 'Format', value: 'Small group cohort (virtual)' },
                { label: 'Who It Is For', value: 'Professional women in career transition' },
                { label: 'Focus Areas', value: 'Personal strategy, AI tools, economic positioning' },
                { label: 'Cohort Size', value: 'Limited seats per cohort' },
                { label: 'Outcome', value: 'A personal and professional strategy you can execute immediately' },
              ].map((item) => (
                <div class="flex gap-4 border-b border-border pb-4 last:border-0 last:pb-0">
                  <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-bold shrink-0 w-28 pt-0.5">{item.label}</p>
                  <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.value}</p>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-border">
              <p class="text-muted text-xs italic">Pricing and cohort dates are shared during the application process. Seats are limited and filled on a rolling basis.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-28" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, #0f172a);"></div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── WHO THIS IS FOR ───────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Sound Familiar?</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">
          This is what it feels like to need a reset.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        {[
          'You are between roles, industries, or identities and the path forward is not clear.',
          'You know AI is changing everything but you do not know where to start or what it means for your specific situation.',
          'You have a strong resume and a real track record, but the market feels like it has shifted under your feet.',
          'You are exhausted from pivoting reactively and ready to build something intentional.',
          'You want a strategy, not just motivation. A plan, not just a pep talk.',
          'You are doing this mostly alone and you are ready to be in a room with women who actually get it.',
        ].map((pain, i) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover flex items-start gap-3 animate-on-scroll" style={`animation-delay:${i * 0.05}s`}>
            <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0 mt-1 text-sm">→</span>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{pain}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── WHAT YOU GET ──────────────────────────────── -->
  <section id="what-you-get" class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.05) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">What You Get</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">
          Not a workshop. A strategic reset.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-3 max-w-lg mx-auto">
          Every element of the SRI is designed to move you from overwhelmed to oriented.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            icon: '🔄',
            title: 'Personal Strategy Session',
            desc: 'You will build a clear, written strategy for your next chapter. Not a vision board. A real plan with priorities, timelines, and decision criteria.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🤖',
            title: 'AI Tools for Your Life',
            desc: 'Learn which AI tools are actually useful for your situation and how to use them for career positioning, productivity, and personal workflow. No jargon. No overwhelm.',
          },
          {
            icon: '📍',
            title: 'Economic Positioning',
            desc: 'Understand how to read the current market, identify where your skills are most valuable, and position yourself to build in an economy that keeps shifting.',
          },
          {
            icon: '🗺️',
            title: 'Work Strategy Blueprint',
            desc: 'A structured framework for evaluating opportunities, negotiating your worth, and designing work that actually fits your life and your goals.',
          },
          {
            icon: '👥',
            title: 'Small Group Cohort',
            desc: 'A curated, intimate group of professional women in similar transitions. Real conversation, shared tools, and the kind of community that does not let you stay stuck.',
          },
          {
            icon: '✅',
            title: 'Immediate Next Steps',
            desc: 'You will leave every session with a specific action, not just insight. The SRI is built for execution, not just reflection.',
          },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover animate-on-scroll">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">{item.icon}</span>
            <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold text-lg mb-3">{item.title}</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── THE TRANSFORMATION ────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-14 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">The Shift</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl text-light">What changes when you reset with intention.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-border max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
        {[
          { before: 'Reacting to every job posting with anxiety', after: 'Applying strategically to roles that align with your blueprint' },
          { before: 'Avoiding AI because it feels overwhelming', after: 'Using AI tools confidently to work smarter and position better' },
          { before: 'Feeling behind in a shifting economy', after: 'Understanding exactly where your skills are most valuable right now' },
          { before: 'Navigating transition alone and exhausted', after: 'Moving forward inside a community of women who are building alongside you' },
          { before: 'Unclear on what you actually want next', after: 'A written strategy with priorities, timelines, and a clear next step' },
          { before: 'Waiting for the right moment to start', after: 'In motion, with a plan, and accountability to keep going' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-surface p-6 flex gap-6 items-start">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-400/70 mb-2">Before</p>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">{item.before}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-teal-DEFAULT/40 text-xl shrink-0 mt-3">→</div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="text-xs font-body font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-DEFAULT mb-2">After</p>
              <p class="text-light text-sm font-medium">{item.after}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── ABOUT NIKKI ───────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.05) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-wide relative z-10 animate-on-scroll">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 items-center border border-teal-DEFAULT/20 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-surface">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 h-full min-h-[400px] overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src="/images/sri/nikki-sri.jpg"
            alt="Nikki Cates, CEO and Founder of Strategic Transformations"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Bio -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 p-10 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-teal-DEFAULT text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] mb-4">Your Facilitator</p>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl text-light mb-4">Nikki Cates</h2>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">CEO &amp; Founder, Strategic Transformations · Army Veteran · Womanist Scholar · Published Author</p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Nikki Cates is a Structural Recalibration Strategist who has spent over 15 years helping individuals and organizations navigate high-stakes transitions. She is the creator of the UNMASK Framework, a proprietary diagnostic methodology used by leaders, organizations, and professionals to surface hidden structural strain and build a path forward.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
            The Strategic Reset Intensive was built because Nikki kept seeing the same thing: brilliant, capable professional women navigating major transitions without the structural tools to do it strategically. The SRI is the answer to that gap.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── FINAL CTA ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 50% 50%, rgba(13,148,136,0.07) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-narrow relative z-10 text-center animate-on-scroll">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl text-light mb-5 leading-tight">
        Ready to stop reacting<br/>
        <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT">and start building?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Seats in each cohort are limited. Apply now to be considered for the next available cohort and take the first step toward your strategic reset.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href={sriApplyUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-teal text-base !py-4 !px-8">
          Apply for the Next Cohort &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-muted text-xs mt-6">Not sure if this is right for you? Take the <a href="#" class="text-teal-DEFAULT hover:underline">AI Readiness Quiz</a> first.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
